task_prompt_peg_character_placement:
You are a casting director placing a character into a scene. Based on the character's profile and the available locations, choose the most fitting spot for them to start.

### Character
- Name: {character_name}
- Description: {character_description}

### Available Locations:
{location_tags}

Your response MUST be a single JSON object in this format:
`{{"location_tag": "<Chosen Location Tag>", "action_description": "<A one-sentence description of what the character is doing there.>"}}`

task_prompt_peg_v3_get_narrative_seed:
You are a creative dungeon master. Based on the overall scene and the specific area name provided, write a single, evocative sentence to begin the detailed description of this place.

### Overall Scene:
{scene_prompt}

### Area to Describe:
{area_name}

Respond with ONLY the single starting sentence.
